|                        AppCompatActivity                     |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| (Android SDK base class; methods inherited)                  |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
                          ▲
                          │
        +-----------------+-----------------+
        │                                   │
+-------------------------+     +-------------------------+
|     AddItemActivity     |     |    EditItemActivity     |
|-------------------------|     |-------------------------|
| - itemName: String      |     | - itemId: int          |
| - itemDescription: String|    | - itemName: String     |
| - status: String        |     | - itemDescription: String |
| - borrower: String      |     | - status: String       |
|-------------------------|     | - borrower: String    |
| + addItem()             |     | + editItem()          |
| + validateInput()       |     | + updateItem()        |
| + saveItem()            |     | + deleteItem()        |
+-------------------------+     +-------------------------+

        Inheritance (from AppCompatActivity)

+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|                        ItemList                              |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| - items: List<Item>                                          |
| - filterType: String (e.g., "All", "Available", "Borrowed") |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| + displayItems()                                             |
| + filterItems()                                              |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+

        Aggregates many Items

+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|                            Item                                |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| - id: int                                                    |
| - name: String                                               |
| - description: String                                        |
| - status: String ("Available" / "Borrowed")                   |
| - borrower: String (nullable if available)                     |
| - dimensions: Dimensions                                       |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| + toggleStatus()                                             |
| + setBorrower(borrowerName: String)                            |
| + getDetails()                                               |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+

        Composition (has Dimensions)

+--------------------------------------------------------------+
|                        Dimensions                            |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| - length: float                                              |
| - width: float                                               |
| - height: float                                              |
|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| + getVolume()                                                |
| + getDimensions()                                            |
+--------------------------------------------------------------+
